OL,3,CBlitz Vega new album to be released on
OL,4,Canniversary of Andy Rourke's death
OL,6,FHe said: "I met Andy about 24 years
OL,7,Fago and Manny from the Stone Roses had
OL,8,Fbrought him down from a gig and we had
OL,9,Fall sorts of people in there from
OL,10,FBonehead from the Oasis and other
OL,11,FMancunian legends.
OL,13,F"Andy was introduced to me and he was
OL,14,Fjust so nice. So we stayed in touch
OL,15,Fover the years and I was playing
OL,16,FCoachella with The Happy Mondays, Andy
OL,17,Fwas DJ'ing and he was saying that we
OL,18,Fshould start a band together at some
OL,19,Fpoint."
