OL,6,FHe continued: "The whole idea of the
OL,7,Fband was to be a touring band and
OL,8,Fthat's the only thing we couldn't do
OL,9,Fbecause Andy was unwell."
OL,11,FWhile the Sandhu and Rourke recorded
OL,12,Fwith the Blitz Vega band at the famous
OL,13,FAbbey Road recording studios, Andy was
OL,14,Fpoorly and had to play sitting down as
OL,15,Fhe was battling cancer and just had an
OL,16,Foperation at the time.
