OL,6,FSandhu said: "I don't know many people
OL,7,Fthat can still play the bass sitting
OL,8,Fdown. And no one picked up on it
OL,9,Fbecause he looked really cool. He
OL,10,Falways looked cool."
OL,12,F"I was sitting with him in the
OL,13,Fhospital in New York and he said
OL,14,F'you've got to do a favour for me,
OL,15,Fyou've got to make sure the album
OL,16,F(Northern Gentleman) comes out and you
OL,17,Ftake it on the road'. He really was a
OL,18,FNorthern Gentleman."
